 <th class="p-3 text-left font-semibold">Maxi-Cosi Pebble 360 Pro</th>
 <th class="p-3 text-left font-semibold">Cybex Cloud T i-Size</th>
 </tr>
 </thead>
 <tbody>
 <tr class="bg-bg-alt/50 border-b border-border">
